                <h2 class="section-title lang-en">Creating content isn't the problem.</h2>
                <p class="lang-pt" style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.2rem">O problema é a falta de sistema.</p>
                <p class="lang-en" style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.2rem">The problem is the lack of system.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-grid">
                <div class="problem-card fade-in">
                    <div class="problem-icon">📉</div>
                    <h3 class="lang-pt">Falta de Distribuição Estratégica</h3>
                    <h3 class="lang-en">Lack of Strategic Distribution</h3>
